Or-and-if: 
  
    
      
        P
        →
        Q
        ≡
        ¬
        P
        ∨
        Q
      
    
    {\displaystyle P\to Q\equiv \neg P\lor Q}
  
Commutativity of antecedents: 
  
    
      
        
          
            (
          
        
