        R
        )
        
          
            )
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle {\big (}P\to (Q\to R){\big )}\equiv {\big (}Q\to (P\to R){\big )}}
  
Distributivity: 
  
    
      
        
          
            (
          
        
        R
        →
        (
        P
        →
        Q
        )
        
          
            )
          
        
